description.en: DAppLinks is a multi-chain decentralised application empowerment platform that serves the public chain, DApp developers, traffic channels and users. On the one hand, the DAppLinks Browser enables the traffic channel, allowing users to directly experience the DApp without importing the private key; on the other hand, the DAppLinks SDK enables the developer to gain the ability to export the multi-chain version of the DApp in one click, greatly reducing the DApp. Development and maintenance costs.
